  <summary date="2021-11-19T19:38:25Z" status="Introduced in House">Restaurant Recovery Fairness Act of 2021

This bill directs the Small Business Administration (SBA) to require applicants for restaurant revitalization grants to reduce waste, fraud, and abuse, and it requires the SBA to submit an oversight and audit plan detailing its policies and procedures with respect to such grants.</summary>
